					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287" rend="visible">
						<summary>The 11th book of Maimonides' Mishneh Torah, i.e. Sefer Neziḳin.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he">Hebrew</textLang>
						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287">
							<locus from="1r" to="88v"/>
							<title xml:lang="en">Mishneh Torah</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">משנה תורה</title>
							<author key="http://viaf.org/viaf/100185495">
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/100185495" xml:lang="en">Maimonides, Moses, 1135-1204</persName>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/100185495" xml:lang="he">משה בן מימון, 1138-1204 </persName>
							</author>
							<colophon xml:lang="he">שלים בסייעתא דשמייא בירח<date when="1353" calendar="Seleucid"> תשרי שנת א'ת'ר'ס'ה' שנין לשטרות</date> יום חד בשבא במדינת <name type="place">אלטוילה </name>יהא סימן טב <name type="person" role="patron">למריה עמרם בי"ר מימון בי"ר עזרא בי"ר סעדיה</name>.<locus n="87r"/>
							</colophon>
							<decoNote type="border">
								<locus from="88r" to="88v"/>An ornamented index to the Mishneh Torah, belonging originally to a different manuscript (of approximately 14th to 15th century).</decoNote>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Paper codex of the 14th century.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="chart">
								<extent>88 folios <dimensions unit="mm" type="leaf">
										<height>262</height>
										<width>195</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>195</height>
										<width>145</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>88 folios (+ 2 unfoliated modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>8 quires of mostly 12 leaves each, marked with catchwords at the end and numbered with Hebrew letters at the beginning and at the end.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Stained.</p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1 " ruledLines="22 23" writtenLines="22 23">
									<p>Uniform layout. Visible ruling with a sharp object (complete).</p>
									<p>Scant marginal notes.</p>
									<p>Chapter numbers given in larger characters.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
